Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Relaxa. Usei o dorso das espadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why'd you have to knock\Ndown all the shipwrights?! - OG}Por que teve que derrubar\N{\i1}todos{\i0} os carpinteiros?!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wow, Zoro is strong! - OG}O Zoro é muito forte!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, well... let's go already! - OG}Tanto faz, vamos logo!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro, por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:17.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Tá.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, I said this way! - OG}Não, por aqui!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could you go in the wrong direction when we're leading the way for you?! A miracle?! - OG}Você nem consegue nos seguir quando estamos\Nte guiando?! Isso é um milagre!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! I'm out... since I'm a rubber man! - OG}Beleza! Saí... já que sou de borracha!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good job! Okay! Take off my cuffs! - OG}Bom trabalho! Agora tira as minhas!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:50.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just wait and see... damn bull and skull...! - OG}Aquele touro e caveira vão se ver comigo!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:59.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were undercover for five years. - OG}Estamos disfarçados há cinco anos.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:04.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please don't worry.\NWe didn't cut corners with our work. - OG}Por favor, não se preocupe.\NLevamos nossos trabalhos de fachada a sério.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I do understand how dispirited you are. - OG}Eu entendo seu desespero.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:14.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No entanto, como não podemos gastar\Nmais tempo com esse assunto,{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we're going to try our best to achieve our goal. - OG}faremos o que for preciso\Npra alcançar nosso objetivo agora.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're thinking of putting up an\Nunwise resistance, I suggest you don't. - OG}Qualquer resistência seria imprudente;\Nnem pense nisso.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You know the name "Cipher Pol," don't you? - OG}Já ouviu falar de "Cipher Pol", não é?{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:32.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's the government's supreme intelligence agency, - OG}As pessoas os conhecem como CP1 até CP8.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:37.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{with eight bases around the world, called CP1 through CP8 by people. - OG}{\q2}São as principais agências de inteligência do\NGoverno Mundial, cada uma com sua própria base.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When the government orders it, they dig\Nup any kind of information in any place. - OG}Quando o governo ordena, eles desenterram\Nqualquer informação de qualquer lugar.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know about them... - OG}Eu ouvi falar deles...{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas só até a CP8.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Right... - OG}Naturalmente.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:54.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porém, nós somos a CP9, a nona Cipher Pol,\Numa unidade que supostamente não existe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since we possess a certain privilege,\Nwe can't reveal ourselves to the public. - OG}Como possuímos certo privilégio,\Nnão podemos agir publicamente.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Privilégio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is in the name of justice to the end, - OG}Em nome da justiça até o fim,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:09.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but when there're citizens who are\Nuncooperative toward the government... - OG}quando há cidadãos que se recusam\Na cooperar com o governo...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we have permission to kill them. - OG}temos autorização para executá-los.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:18.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How selfish...! Justice cannot be a reason for killing! - OG}Que egoísmo! Assassinato em\Nnome da justiça continua sendo assassinato!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:21.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The World Government has\Npartially changed their thinking. - OG}O Governo Mundial reconsiderou\Nparcialmente a questão.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Rather than remaining in fear\Nof the weapon's restoration, - OG}Em vez de viver com medo da restauração da arma,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:32.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{they decided to awaken it to make it into a force of justice\Nthat can end this Great Pirate Era. - OG}decidiram despertá-la para usá-la como uma força\Nda justiça que pode encerrar a Grande Era da Pirataria.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:37.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, you don't want to help them. - OG}Porém, você não quer ajudá-los.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:42.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're saying that you don't want to "save" those people who keep being victimized - OG}Enquanto falamos, piratas estão constantemente\Nvitimando pessoas ao redor do mundo,{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{by pirates around the world. - OG}e mesmo assim você diz que\Nnão quer salvá-las.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:50.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nonsense... If the weapon is restored, the world will only fight over its power. - OG}Que absurdo... Restaure essa arma\Ne o mundo só vai brigar por seu poder.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The damage only keeps growing! - OG}O ciclo de destruição só continua!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It seems that you don't trust\Nthe government, Iceburg-san. - OG}Tenho a impressão de que não confia\Nno governo, Iceburg.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I just know the nature of humans, that's all, lad. - OG}Eu apenas conheço a natureza humana, rapaz.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:16.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Restrain yourself. Just how long are\Nyou going to keep acting like my boss? - OG}Cuide da sua língua.\NEu não trabalho mais pra você.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kaku, verifique o pulso dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:36.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san... To tell you the truth,\Nwe came up with a hypothesis a bit ago. - OG}Iceburg, pra falar a verdade,\Ndesenvolvemos uma hipótese há pouco.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:42.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All you have to do is listen to our\Nhypothesis without saying a word. - OG}Tudo que precisa fazer é ficar quieto\Nenquanto eu explico.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:47.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que seu pulso vai nos revelar a verdade.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:54.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well then, I'll explain the thought\Nprocess leading to our hypothesis. - OG}Então, permita-me elaborar\Ncomo chegamos à nossa hipótese.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:06:01.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{First, we have doubts about your action of passing off the fake to us. - OG}Primeiro, temos dúvidas sobre sua manobra\Nde nos passar a falsificação.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guessed that the culprits\Nwho came after the blueprints - OG}Você deduziu que agentes do governo\Nestavam atrás das plantas,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:08.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{were from the government, so you\Nindicated where the fake was. - OG}então indicou onde a falsa estava.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porém...{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:17.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{if it happened to be someone who had a grudge against you and they just came to kill you, - OG}se fosse alguém que viesse\Nte matar por vingança,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:24.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the real blueprints would lose their owner and they'd no longer be passed down. - OG}as plantas verdadeiras ficariam abandonadas,\Nsem serem passadas adiante.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're not stupid enough not\Nto think about that possibility. - OG}Você não é burro o bastante\Npra ignorar essa possibilidade.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even though you knew that, - OG}Mesmo sabendo disso,{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:35.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you still didn't try to give the\Nreal blueprints to anyone tonight. - OG}você não fez nenhum esforço pra transferir\Nas plantas verdadeiras pra alguém essa noite.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That means you've already\Nentrusted them with someone. - OG}Isso significa que você já\Nas confiou a alguém.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:44.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No mínimo, não estão com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So we think. - OG}É o que acreditamos.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's no use. Don't act up. - OG}É inútil. Não se rebele.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is still only a possibility. - OG}Isso ainda é apenas uma hipótese.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:57.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course, no convincing proof\Ncan be found anywhere. - OG}Claro, não encontramos nenhuma\Nprova convincente.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The past five years of our\Nsurveillance and investigation - OG}Nossa vigilância e investigação\Nnos últimos cinco anos{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,também não revelaram nada em suas ações.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:10.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In addition, the person who is\Nentrusted with the blueprints has to have proper shipbuilding skills. - OG}{\q2}Além disso, a pessoa com as plantas\Nprecisaria ser um carpinteiro naval competente.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, let me continue with our hypothesis. - OG}Com isso, vou contar\No resto da nossa hipótese.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now things are getting more interesting. - OG}É aqui que fica interessante.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:24.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essas são as plantas falsas\Nque você nos passou antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:29.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When I look at them carefully,\Nthere're signatures by the architects. - OG}Olhe de perto e verá\Nas assinaturas dos projetistas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Tom", "Iceburg" e "Cutty Flam".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No final, tem um nome\Nde empresa: "Tom's Workers".{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:41.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você pode ter pensado que enganou\Nseu inimigo com essas falsificações.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:46.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas nunca sonhou que seu inimigo\Nestava escondido tão perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse foi seu erro de cálculo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:53.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To an overnight intruder\Nwho came after the blueprints, - OG}Para um ladrão noturno\Natrás das plantas,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:56.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{these would probably just be trash. - OG}isso provavelmente não teria valor.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:08:00.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But to us, who lived in this town for the past five years, - OG}Mas para nós, que vivemos nesta\Ncidade nos últimos cinco anos,{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,esses nomes dos projetistas são muito interessantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.92,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san, you have a guest. - OG}Iceburg, você tem uma visita.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:13.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tom's Workers, liderada pelo\Nlendário carpinteiro naval Tom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:16.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{was a shipbuilding company\Nthat was full of mysteries. - OG}era uma empresa de construção naval\Nenvolta em mistério.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:21.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I think it used to be on this island, but there's no list of workers or company registration. - OG}Parece que existiu nesta ilha,\Nmas não há registros de funcionários ou da empresa.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:26.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just finding out the fact that you were Tom's disciple was quite hard. - OG}Descobrir que você era aprendiz de Tom\Njá foi muito difícil.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{According to the report by the government,\NTom had only two disciples. - OG}De acordo com o relatório do governo,\NTom tinha apenas dois aprendizes.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:38.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And a government official verified that one of them died in an accident that happened eight years ago. - OG}E um oficial do governo confirmou que\Num deles morreu num acidente oito anos atrás.{Gal/Z/JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:47.88,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you know... that Tom's\Nviolent disciple Cutty Flam died? - OG}Ficou sabendo? O aprendiz violento do Tom,\NCutty Flam, morreu.{WF/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:53.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, I remember hearing\Nthis name Cutty Flam before. - OG}Porém, lembro de ter ouvido\No nome Cutty Flam antes.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:09:00.14,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san, you have a guest. He said\Nyou'd know who if I told you "Cutty Flam." - OG}{\q2}Iceburg, você tem uma visita. Ele disse\Nque saberia quem é se eu mencionasse "Cutty Flam".{WF/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:07.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was about four years ago, a little while\Nafter we started going undercover here. - OG}Foi há cerca de quatro anos,\Npouco depois de começarmos o disfarce.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:12.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There was a man who came through the\NGalley-La Company's gate to see you. - OG}Havia um homem que veio pelo portão\Nda Galley-La Company pra te ver.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:15.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele usou esse nome apenas uma vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu também me lembro.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Me, too. - OG}Eu também.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.87,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Devo mandá-lo entrar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.54,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... turn him away. - OG}Não. Dispense-o.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em outras palavras...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:40.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O outro aprendiz de Tom, Cutty Flam, ainda está vivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e mora nesta cidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,depois de mudar seu nome para Franky!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.95,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a roundabout way of meeting. - OG}Que jeito complicado\Nde se encontrar.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:06.71,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're these? Hey, they're the blueprints\Nfor the ancient weapon. - OG}Essas não são as plantas que vimos\Ndaquela arma ancestral?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.71,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't use the name Cutty Flam from now on. - OG}Nunca mais use o nome Cutty Flam.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.71,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.21,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's only a matter of time before I get targeted. - OG}É questão de tempo até\Nvirem atrás de mim.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.76,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Leave the island with them... Franky. - OG}Leve-as e saia da ilha, Franky.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seems like there's no mistake about it. - OG}É claro como o dia.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:27.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I never thought that you and that guy\Nwere connected like that. - OG}Nunca imaginei que você e aquele\Ncara estavam conectados assim.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's true that no matter\Nhow much we investigated, -OG}É verdade que por mais que\Ninvestigássemos o Franky,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we couldn't figure out his real identity. - OG}não conseguíamos descobrir sua verdadeira identidade.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But because he was a ship demolition worker and because of his behavior, we paid no attention to him. - OG}Mas o ignoramos porque era apenas\Num desmontador de navios mal-humorado.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see... Involving a dead person was indeed a perfect way - OG}De fato... Como nossa especulação veio inteiramente dos fatos conhecidos,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{to exploit our blind spot, since our speculation was generated only from the facts. - OG}envolver uma "pessoa morta"\Nexplorou perfeitamente nosso ponto cego.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:50.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Franky Family would come\Nto the shipyard to sell lumber. - OG}A Franky Family vinha\Nao estaleiro vender madeira.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:55.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So there were many chances for you to make\Nan arrangement to give him the blueprints. - OG}Então você teve muitas oportunidades\Npra arranjar a entrega das plantas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:11:00.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, come to think of it, you could say that he was a neighbor who kept a safe distance. - OG}Pensando bem, ele era mais como\Num vizinho que mantinha distância segura.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não tem as plantas com você,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:08.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{it makes sense that you held firm. - OG}faz sentido que tenha se mantido firme.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it was your only fellow disciple\Nwhom you entrusted them with, - OG}Se confiou ao seu\Ncolega de aprendizado,{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{it's also understandable that you didn't entrust them with any of the foremen at Galley-La. - OG}é compreensível que nunca tenha dado\Na nenhum dos capatazes da Galley-La.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, our speculations\Nare connected as one line. - OG}Depois de toda essa especulação, tudo se encaixa.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In addition... - OG}Além disso...{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{your pounding blood proved it to be true! - OG}seu pulso acelerado prova tudo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:30.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you really sure this is the right way? - OG}Tem certeza que é por aqui?{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't you say that! - OG}Você não tem moral pra falar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They've been hurt quite badly. - OG}Estão bem machucados.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Over there! That door is the one!\NThere's no mistake! - OG}Ali! Tem que ser aquela porta!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Many people are down over there, too! - OG}Muita gente caída ali também!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:57.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, you go ahead! Ahead of us!\NCut down the door and make a dash! - OG}Certo! Vai na frente,\Nderruba a porta e invade!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:57.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Vai na frente!\N– Vai na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que droga?! Não me dêem ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:11.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You idiot! Wrong room! It's the next room! - OG}Seu idiota! Sala errada! É a próxima!{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, the next room? - OG}Ah, é a próxima?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:18.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, não é culpa sua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:21.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So many things are happening tonight. - OG}Muita coisa aconteceu essa noite.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:26.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're only human. It's just natural that\Nyou couldn't hide your consternation. - OG}Você é humano, afinal. É natural\Nque não conseguisse esconder sua consternação.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:30.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I appreciate what you've done for us. We're done with you. - OG}Agradecemos o que fez por nós,\Nmas acabou.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos encontrar o Franky logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus desgraçados...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê a Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How bothersome...! - OG}Que incômodo...{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! Finalmente te encontrei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy! Onde diabos você estava?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:10.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Robin! I'm glad that I could see you again! - OG}Robin! Que bom te ver de novo!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera... O que está acontecendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, well, well... - OG}Ora, ora...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I-Iceburg-san... - OG}I-Iceburg...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:33.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Que droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:39.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:49.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie... Por que... não fugiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's going on? - OG}O que está acontecendo aqui?!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This looks... as if... - OG}Isso parece quase... como se...{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{they're the culprits who tried to kill you! - OG}eles fossem os culpados\Nque tentaram te matar!{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:16.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you guys dressed like that?! - OG}Vocês! Que roupas são essas?!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:21.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Kalifa...! Blueno...! Kaku...! Lucci...! - OG}Ei! Kalifa! Blueno! Kaku! Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop joking, you bastards! - OG}Parem de me zoar, seus malditos!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:30.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são dos carpinteiros\Nque estavam com você! Certo?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it,\NI know that square long-nosed guy. -OG}Ah, verdade... Já vi aquele cara\Ndo nariz comprido e quadrado.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:37.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Could this mean... that the assassination was an inside job? - OG}Então... o assassinato\Nfoi coisa de gente de dentro?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? O que quer dizer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:45.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Paulie, to tell you the truth, we're government intelligence agents. - OG}Paulie, a verdade é que somos\Nagentes de inteligência do governo.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:50.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, you'd forgive us if we apologized, right? - OG}Bom, nos perdoaria se pedíssemos desculpa, né?{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:56.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were fellow shipwrights who worked\Ntogether building ships every day. - OG}Estivemos construindo navios juntos\Ntodo dia como colegas.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:15:01.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you can't believe me because this is too sudden, shall I step on Iceburg's face or something? - OG}Sei que é repentino, então se eu pisar\Nna cara do Iceburg, você acreditaria?{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem de zoar! Já chega...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:15.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After all, the bull-masked man's voice I\Nheard earlier is the same voice as yours! - OG}Afinal, sua voz é a mesma\Ndo homem mascarado de touro!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:21.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga, seu maldito! Então você fala normalmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ousam zombar da gente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pipe Hitch Knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:50.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda não aprendeu a lição, Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, cara da corda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:03.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop this pointless resistance. - OG}Resistir é inútil.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:19.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dominamos técnicas\Nalém dos limites humanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:25.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After years of training, these techniques, called the "Six Powers," allow human bodies to be a match for weapons. - OG}{\q2}Após anos de treino, essas técnicas, as Seis Formas,\Ntornam corpos humanos tão letais quanto armas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:29.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once one masters them, he alone\Nis as strong as 100 people together. - OG}Quem as domina ganha\Na força de 100 pessoas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.14,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo! Don't get carried away with the gambling. - OG}Não exagera nas apostas.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:41.60,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You dummy! I was lucky today.\NThat's why I'm treating you guys! - OG}Idiota, tive sorte hoje!\NPor isso estou pagando pra vocês!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:44.82,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Blueno! Bring us more alcohol! - OG}Blueno! Mais bebida!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.28,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:57.54,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kalifa! You're dressed like that again?! - OG}Ei, Kalifa! Vestida assim {\i0}de novo{\i1}?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:03.95,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it, Paulie. Just don't look at her. Right? - OG}Para, Paulie. Apenas desvie o olhar. Tá?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you guys...? - OG}O que há com vocês...?{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, esqueçam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Either way, you're gonna be killed. - OG}Infelizmente, meu amigo...{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is sad, but my friend... - OG}você vai morrer de qualquer jeito.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci, seu...!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it! You jerk! - OG}Para com isso, desgraçado!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:41.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? It's not working at all! - OG}O quê? Não fez nada!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que incômodo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:01.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele desapareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:13.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you had a flesh-and-blood body, you would've\Ngotten a hole in your neck and died instantly... - OG}Se tivesse um corpo de carne e osso,\Nestaria morto com um furo no pescoço...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,homem de borracha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está fazendo, Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:01.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você ia matá-lo, não é?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:05.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought you were all shipwright\Nfriends who worked together! - OG}Vocês não construíam navios juntos?!{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:12.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Up until earlier, yes.\NBut that's no longer the case. - OG}Até esta noite, sim.\NMas isso acabou.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then you guys really are traitors?! - OG}Então vocês realmente\Ntraíram eles?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ótimo, então!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, I promised him - OG}No mínimo, eu prometi a ele...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:26.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that we'd beat the crap out of those\Nwho're trying to kill Ice pops together! - OG}que bateríamos juntos em quem estivesse\Ntentando matar o velho Ice!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:31.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que está do lado do Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I have some business\Nwith you people, too! - OG}Porque eu também tenho assunto com vocês!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:38.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Robin! Why are you with jerks like them?! - OG}Ei, Robin! Por que está com esses idiotas?!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:42.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you wanna leave us, tell us the reason! - OG}Se quer sair da tripulação, diz o motivo!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:47.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão! Eles disseram que trabalham\Npro governo! Então por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're not listening, are you? - OG}Vocês não escutam bem, né?{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I did say goodbye to Cook and Doctor. - OG}Já me despedi do cozinheiro\Ne do médico.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não contaram?{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:20:00.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contaram! Mas eu também não aceito!\NPor quê, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra realizar meu desejo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:08.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A wish that can never come true if I'm with you! - OG}Um desejo que nunca se realizará\Nse eu ficar com vocês!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:14.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In order to make it happen, I don't\Ncare what sacrifices need to be made! - OG}Pra alcançá-lo, farei qualquer sacrifício!{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:21.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's why... you set your friends up\Nas assassins without hesitation? - OG}Então... incriminar seus amigos por assassinato\Nnem te fez pensar duas vezes?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's that wish of yours?! - OG}Qual é esse desejo?!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não preciso contar.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é loucura!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That woman is...! - OG}Porque ela é...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you out of your mind, Nico Robin?! - OG}Você perdeu o juízo, Nico Robin?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:36.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem noção do que está prestes a fazer?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:39.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You no longer have the right to say anything! - OG}Você não tem mais o direito\Nde me dar lição sobre nada!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fique de boca fechada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san! - OG}Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:54.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar ninguém atrapalhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:13.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Robin! O que está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you really mean it?! - OG}Está falando sério?!{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:18.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! O que aconteceu com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:28.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você realmente é nossa inimiga agora?! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but I need you guys to stop now. - OG}Desculpem, mas vou ter que encerrar isso.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:43.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to find an important person now, so we're in a hurry. - OG}Temos uma pessoa importante pra encontrar\Nagora, então estamos com pressa.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We no longer have business here. - OG}Não temos mais nada pra fazer aqui...{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't have any business\Nwith you guys, either. - OG}nem temos assunto com nenhum de vocês.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:56.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa, quanto tempo resta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:57.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dois minutos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:03.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know this is sudden, but this building\Nis to be set aflame in two minutes. - OG}Perdoem a surpresa, mas este prédio\Nserá incendiado em dois minutos.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fire is an effective tool\Nfor destroying various types of evidence. - OG}Fogo é uma ferramenta eficaz\Npra destruir todo tipo de evidência.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:18.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you don't wanna burn to death,\Nyou should leave the building immediately. - OG}Se não querem morrer queimados,\Ndeviam sair do prédio imediatamente.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, é claro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:26.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that is, if you could. - OG}isso supondo que consigam.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like they intend to eliminate us. - OG}Parece que planejam nos matar.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It also seems that Nico Robin\Nwants to be on their side. - OG}Também está claro de que lado\Na Nico Robin escolheu ficar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:43.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, were you able to accept\NRobin's leaving the ship? - OG}Luffy, você aceita que\Na Robin deixou o navio?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:49.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could I?! - OG}Claro que não!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:53.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, you don't have to shout like that.}Não precisa gritar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:57.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em breve, vários cômodos no primeiro\Nandar vão pegar fogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:00.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, the culprits are pirates. - OG}Bom, a culpa é dos piratas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:02.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Things like this can happen. - OG}Essas coisas acontecem.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus desgraçados...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that you do as you please\Nwhile pretending someone else did it... - OG}Fazem o que querem enquanto\Ncolocam a culpa nos outros...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:12.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You sure have bad taste! - OG}Que falta de caráter!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:17.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês já são criminosos. Sem prejuízo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:25.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go on ahead and leave now. - OG}Vou indo na frente.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:29.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you completed your job. Thanks. - OG}Certo. Você cumpriu sua parte. Obrigado.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:32.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou permitir!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:34.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Adeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Robin!\N– Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:40.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't... - OG}Não...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,deixem a Nico Robin ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:48.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where're you going this time...\Nwhen we finally found you?! - OG}Pra onde vai dessa vez...\Nquando finalmente te encontramos?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:51.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai da minha frente, desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:51.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:03.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que os corpos deles são tão duros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:06.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossos corpos são bem treinados.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:09.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can raise our bodies' solidity\Nto be as hard as iron crust. - OG}Podemos elevar a solidez dos nossos corpos\Nao nível do ferro.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:14.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, that's not to say\Ndefense is all we can do. - OG}Porém, não é só defesa\Nque temos.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:17.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse pra sair da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Paper Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:32.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's dodging all the punches... when he's that big! - OG}Está desviando de todos os socos...\Ne ele é enorme!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.83,0:24:35.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está flutuando como papel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.53,0:24:40.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:42.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:47.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu filho da...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.25,0:24:52.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.52,0:24:55.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:55.05,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.36,0:24:59.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele também desapareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.57,0:25:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If your legs are so tremendously strong\Nthat it appears as if you disappeared... - OG}Quando suas pernas são tão tremendamente fortes\Na ponto de dar a ilusão de sumir...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.29,0:25:05.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.07,0:25:07.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Moon Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.61,0:25:11.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...you can even kick the air and float. - OG}...você também consegue chutar o ar e flutuar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.21,0:25:14.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está voando! Que diabos...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.17,0:25:18.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– And...\N– And... - OG}– E tem também...\N– E tem também...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.04,0:25:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– ...Tempest Kick.\N– ...Tempest Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.80,0:25:24.83,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Um ataque cortante...?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.83,0:25:26.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês dois...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.11,0:25:27.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Abaixem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.02,0:25:27.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.23,0:25:44.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.07,0:25:47.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did they just cut the wall by kicking?! - OG}Os chutes deles realmente cortaram a parede?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.63,0:25:50.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's possible if you can kick fast\Nenough to cause a gust of sharp wind. - OG}É possível chutando rápido o bastante\Npra criar uma rajada cortante.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.86,0:25:52.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We call it Tempest Kick. - OG}Chamamos de Tempest Kick.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.33,0:26:02.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos conhecemos no seu navio, não é, Roronoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.71,0:26:08.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You aren't a shipwright, then? - OG}Então não é um carpinteiro de verdade, né?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.81,0:26:13.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, could that assessment\Nof our ship you made be... - OG}Então, quando você avaliou\Nnosso navio, aquilo foi...?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.13,0:26:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Unfortunately, I made the\Nassessment of the ship seriously. - OG}Infelizmente pra vocês,\Navalie aquele navio seriamente.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.60,0:26:20.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's indeed unfortunate. - OG}Isso {\i1}sim{\i0} é lamentável!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.59,0:26:30.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Luffy!\N– Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.99,0:26:39.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vá, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.45,0:26:42.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're not done talking yet! - OG}Ainda preciso falar com você!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.28,0:26:47.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, we are. I'll never see you guys again. - OG}Não. Acabou.\NVocês nunca mais vão me ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.25,0:26:49.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.41,0:27:01.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Corre e pega a Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.65,0:27:14.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Roronoa! You're quite confident,\Naren't you, taking your eyes off of me? - OG}Roronoa, deve ser bem confiante\Npra tirar os olhos de mim.{Z/Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.82,0:27:20.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:25.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.19,0:27:32.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't need bullets to\Nshoot through human bodies. - OG}Não precisamos de balas pra\Nperfurar o corpo humano.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.68,0:27:42.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu... desgraçado...! Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.06,0:27:45.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy got caught so easily! - OG}Ele capturou o Luffy tão fácil!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.65,0:27:48.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vá, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:57.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Robin!\N– Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.33,0:28:10.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.21,0:28:18.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.54,0:28:21.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.18,0:28:32.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como podem ser tão fortes?{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.57,0:28:35.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vocês são?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.23,0:28:38.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've lived in a different environment. - OG}Viemos de mundos diferentes.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.59,0:28:42.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ever since we, CP9 members, can remember, - OG}Desde que nós, membros da CP9,\Nnos entendemos por gente,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.24,0:28:45.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we've been prepared to risk\Nour lives for the government - OG}estivemos preparados pra arriscar\Nnossas vidas pelo governo...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.95,0:28:50.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and trained to surpass the\Nlimits of human abilities. - OG}e treinamos pra superar\Nos limites das habilidades humanas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.29,0:28:56.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As a result, we've mastered the superhuman\Ntechniques called the Six Powers. - OG}Como resultado, dominamos as técnicas\Nsobrehumanas das Seis Formas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.89,0:28:59.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure you've fully learned by now - OG}Agora tenho certeza que entenderam{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.96,0:29:04.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that the four of us, who have been entrusted with the World Government's vital tasks, - OG}que nós quatro, encarregados das\Ntarefas vitais do Governo Mundial,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.97,0:29:11.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{are in a whole different league\Nfrom you guys, a mere pirate group. - OG}estamos em um nível completamente diferente\Nde vocês, meros piratas!{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.27,0:29:23.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um segredo de Estado.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.96,0:29:28.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not a matter that people\Nlike you can get involved in. - OG}Algo assim não é da conta\Nde gente como vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.51,0:29:31.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.23,0:29:35.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's about time for the igniters\Nto go off. We have to hurry, too. - OG}Os detonadores estão quase disparando.\NTemos que nos apressar também.{Gal}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.81,0:29:36.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.31,0:29:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas essa é uma ocasião rara.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.35,0:29:42.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me show you something\Ninteresting before we go. - OG}Vou mostrar algo interessante\Nantes de irmos.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.52,0:29:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma fruta do diabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.02,0:29:49.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual será?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.40,0:30:01.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lucci... What the...? - OG}Lucci... Seu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.32,0:30:05.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Fruta Gato-Gato:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.13,0:30:11.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Leopardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.29,0:30:14.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um humano leopardo...{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.88,0:30:16.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ele é enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.12,0:30:20.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's with that appearance?! - OG}Por que está com essa aparência?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.18,0:30:23.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos é você?!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=17}===============================DIALOGUE============================
